Bludgers' Hill
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:nickname for the site of 2NZEF headquarters (Maadi near Cairo)
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: cf. Daffodil Hill
Pronunciation:
Notes: WW2
